snippet.title: Firewall Ultra - Reveal Trailer | PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10003761

The next evolution in the Firewall franchise is coming to PlayStation®VR2.

Enlist as an elite contractor and squad up for PVP and PVE multiplayer missions in Firewall Ultra, a tactical first-person shooter in development by First Contact Entertainment for PS VR2.

Wishlist now on PlayStation Store.

PS5 and PS VR2 required to play. PS VR2 is not for use by children under age 12. Internet connection & PS Plus membership required for online multiplayer. PS Plus is subject to a recurring subscription fee taken automatically until cancellation. Full terms: play.st/psplus-usageterms
